{"tid":1640050,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"AC米蘭炒基安保奴","createTime":"2019-10-08T23:32:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-11T05:28:01.000Z","uid":16659,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"ac66e4a1e53ee39266a3604320eae44bffb3aba2","tid":1640050,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T23:32:55.000Z","msg":"【Now Sports-體育】意甲名牌AC米蘭周二公佈，與教練基安保奴分道揚鑣，即時生效。<br />\n<br />\nAC米蘭教練基安保奴（Marco Giampaolo）早已聞到魷魚香，趁國際賽周期被炒，結束短短111日的賓主關係。<br />\n<br />\n「球會宣佈基安保奴離開一隊教職，並對其工作表示感激，祝他日後一切順利。」紅黑軍團官方聲明寫道。<br />\n<br />\n52歲的基安保奴今夏取代加度素執教，但開季7場僅得3勝4負，排名第13，成績慘不忍睹，比降班區多3分而已。<br />\n<br />\n據知，曾教國際米蘭和費倫天拿的派奧利，有望成為A米新帥，目前談判已進入最後階段。"},{"pid":"2c5db0dcf009d0e1ff3f7b0c14da68510fc9b3fe","tid":1640050,"uid":199590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T23:43:29.000Z","msg":"幾時到so9"},{"pid":"8ca84a14f5abc78bfcad41772ab04951a9409a63","tid":1640050,"uid":173852,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T23:44:49.000Z","msg":"來吧爺爺！"},{"pid":"2368f3faa9e6de1df1e993f9e5f9d5f64eb223b2","tid":1640050,"uid":16659,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T23:47:25.000Z","msg":"炒左換個更廢係咩玩法<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80d2f2b1c9bbe173269b0facf14db909031aaa70","tid":1640050,"uid":138762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2c5db0dcf009d0e1ff3f7b0c14da68510fc9b3fe","tid":1640050,"uid":199590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T23:43:29.000Z","msg":"幾時到so9"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T23:51:08.000Z","msg":"比降班區多3分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />勁過暴聯都炒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f00206eeca4439c20182f689dac6958ae5af0ca3","tid":1640050,"uid":184581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T00:05:52.000Z","msg":"核彈<img src=\"/asset